<br>
We had 15 members of both Alliance of Heroes and Tribunal of Antiquities show up at Lavastorm at the appointed hour.  After about 30 mins of organizing and general pre-raid business, we were off to SOL B.  The roughest part of our adventure was getting to the staging area.  Despite a few folks getting lost (it always happens!), our only death, and my scouting, which brought back about 6 mobs to the staging area, we managed to not lose our heads and got things quickly under control.<br>
<br>
We ran over the lava to the break in area where, after some last minute instructions, I started pulling the big boys. Our first victim was none other than King Tranix himself! Several times I pulled 2 and once 3 giants.  <br>
<br>
Thanks to everyone's cooperation, Aazuma's calm-under-fire charming of about half the giants and Waubau's never-give-up slowing we took every giant in the zone within 90 minutes AND without a single death!<br>
<br>
Good job all!<br>
<br>
Gloro Lisk<br>
